fields.name: Large woven lampshade
fields.description: One of a kind handwoven lampshade using a mixture of luxury and rescued wools. The frame is also rescued and upcycled. Please note this listing is for the lampshade only.

fields.description: This abstract landscape tapestry is full of rich colour and texture. Made using high quality fibers along with rescued yarns, including velvet ribbons, wool roving, recycled cottons, hand dyed silk gauze.
